name: 2024 American Silver Eagle .999 Fine Silver in Direct Fit Air Tite with our Certificate of Authenticity Dollar Uncirculated US Mint
small_description: 2024 American Silver Eagle - $1 Legal US Tender - 1 oz of .999 Fine Silver - Comes in Direct Fit Air-Tite - Now with our Certificate of Authenticity!
full_description: 2024 U.S. Silver Eagle Gem Brilliant Uncirculated in Plastic Air-Tite Holder with Certificate of Authenticity Gem Brilliant Uncirculated 2024 American Silver Eagle Shipped to you in a plastic Air-Tite holder. Now with Certificate of Authenticity! The reverse side of 2024 1 oz Silver Eagles features the new soaring bald eagle. In this visual, Emily Damstra has captured the bald eagle in the midst of one of its natural activities. Soaring in flight with its wings flexed, the bald eagle clutches a large oak branch in its talons that it no doubt intends to use in the construction of its nest. The obverse (heads) features a refreshed depiction of Adolph A. Weinman's full-length figure of Liberty in full stride, enveloped in folds of the flag, with her right hand extended and branches of laurel and oak in her left. In 2021, the United States Mint returned to its original historical assets to render a closer reflection of Weinman’s original vision that includes the addition of his traditional artist mark that continues to this day. Images are temporary stock photos and will be updated when more images are released from the US Mint.

full_description: "Presenting the 1909 S VDB Lincoln Wheat Cent 1 oz Pure .999 Copper Round Bullion Coin, a tribute to a significant moment in American numismatic history. Crafted meticulously from high-quality, pure .999 copper, this bullion coin is a sought-after addition to any copper collector's or investor's portfolio. The coin's obverse proudly features the 1909 S VDB Lincoln Wheat Cent design, a highly valuable and coveted design in the world of coin collecting. The design boasts a portrait of President Abraham Lincoln, a symbol of American resilience and unity, and the initials 'VDB,' representing the designer Victor David Brenner. This design encapsulates a unique period in American coinage, making this copper round a piece of history. Each coin is expertly minted from 99.9% pure copper, offering exceptional authenticity and long-term value. The coin's substantial size, 39mm in diameter, allows for an intricate depiction of the Lincoln Wheat Cent design, adding to its visual appeal and historical accuracy. To ensure its long-lasting preservation, each coin is encapsulated in a protective capsule. This protective measure helps maintain the coin's condition, allowing you to appreciate its intricate design for years to come. Each coin is accompanied by a Certificate of Authenticity (COA) from Heavenly Metals, guaranteeing the coin's .999 copper purity and origin, giving peace of mind to collectors and investors. Invest in the 1909 S VDB Lincoln Wheat Cent 1 oz Pure .999 Copper Round Bullion Coin and own a piece of American numismatic history. Secure this representation of a coveted American coin today."

name: One Year Rarities Coin Collection, Genuine United States Minted Coins, Americana Collectible, Certificate of Authenticity – American Coin Treasures
small_description: COLLECTIBLE – Coin designs that were minted for only one year make this a fun collectible. The One Year Rarities Collection contains the Lincoln Steel Penny minted only in 1943, the four Lincoln Bicentennial Pennies minted only in 2009, the four Westward Journey Nickels, and the Bicentennial Quarter, Half Dollar and Dollar. A great set for a beginning collector or advanced hobbyist. Coins are matted on an 8 by 10 inch collectible card which displays obverse and reverse. - QUALITY & DETAIL - In 1943 the Lincoln Penny was minted in steel due to the copper shortage during World War II. The 2009 Lincoln Bicentennial Pennies were minted to celebrate the 200 year anniversary of Lincoln's birth. Each penny shows a different reverse containing an important stage of Lincoln's life. The Westward Journey nickels were minted to honor Lewis and Clark's journey. The 1976 Bicentennial Series honors the Colonial drummer, Independence Hall and the Liberty Bell. - CERTIFICATE OF AUTHENTICITY - Includes a genuine Certificate of Authenticity. The certificate attests to the fact that the coins in this piece are genuine United States coins. Genuine United States coins were produced in limited quantities by the U.S. Government, then authenticated and inspected for quality by a professional numismatist, and certified in collectible condition. - GREAT GIFT - Comes packaged, perfect for the collector, your dad, husband, boyfriend, brother, sister, daughter, son, mother, father or special someone. Great for birthdays, Christmas, Father’s Day, special events, graduation, anniversaries and retirements. Coins are a perfect gift as they detail time and spirit through their obverse and reverse designs, images, wording and dates. Coins make fun keepsakes for travel, special events and holidays. Coins are historical, educational and collectible. - OUR PROMISE - Items include a 30 day money back guarantee and a 1-Year parts & labor manufacturer's warranty. We will repair or replace, at our discretion, any defective product for a period of 1-year from the date of purchase. Items will have readable dates. American Coin Treasures specializes in coin gifts, collectibles, jewelry, stamps and novelty items. American Coin Treasures collections of coins, jewelry, pocket knives and graded coins makes it a one stop site for all your gift needs.
full_description: Looking for historical, educational and collectible coins for yourself or for gifting? Look no further! A meaningful and lovely treasure to keep that brings back history and culture. American Coin Treasures Colorized $2 Bill This is one collectible you'll have to see, to believe! The result is a dazzling work of art and a spectacular currency collectible displayed in a deluxe portfolio.
